      • executePlugin

        public void executePlugin(java.lang.String plugin_name,
                          java.lang.String format,
                          java.lang.String path_filein,

                          java.lang.String[] options,
                          boolean debug)
        Will process the Text extraction depending on the given parameters.

        Will get the appropriate Corpoplugin by analysing the user input

        Parameters:
        plugin_name - String the name of the plugin being used for the extraction
        format - String Format of the file which you are going to process
        path_filein - String path to the original file
        path_fileout - String [optional] Path to the processed file
        options - String[] [optional] Eventual options of a given plugin;
        debug - true to display debug information
